[{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0577","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0577.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0813","title":"Cfingerd ALLOW_EXECUTION 本地权限提升漏洞","description":"Cfingerd（finger协议守护进程实现）存在特权管理不当漏洞。当启用 ALLOW_EXECUTION 选项时，系统未能在代表用户执行程序前正确丢弃 root 权限，导致本地攻击者可通过请求服务执行任意程序来获取 root 权限，进而完全控制目标系统。该漏洞影响运行 Cfingerd 的各类 Unix/Linux 系统，CVSS 评分 7.2，危害等级高。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0813"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-10T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:49:06.607","remediation":"立即升级 cfingerd 至 1.4.0 或更高版本（当前最新为 1.4.3），该版本已修复执行外部程序时未正确丢弃 root 权限的安全缺陷。如无法升级，在 cfingerd.conf 中将 ALLOW_EXECUTION 设置为 false 以禁用该功能，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["https://exchange.xforce.ibmcloud.com/vulnerabilities/CVE-1999-0813"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0577.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0216","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0216.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0674","title":"BSD 系列操作系统 profil 系统调用本地权限提升漏洞","description":"BSD 系统 profil(2) 系统调用存在安全缺陷，本地攻击者可通过 profile 与 execve 的组合调用，在程序执行过程中修改其内部数据空间，进而导致进程行为异常或权限提升。此漏洞影响 NetBSD 1.4、OpenBSD 2.5 及 Solaris 7.0 等多个 Unix 类操作系统，攻击者需具备本地用户账户权限才能利用。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.2,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0674"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.237","remediation":"NetBSD 用户应升级至 1.4.1 及以上版本，OpenBSD 用户应升级至 2.6 及以上版本，Solaris 用户应安装对应操作系统补丁包或升级至 Solaris 8/9，以修复 profil(2) 系统调用中关于 profiling 与 execve 的内部数据空间修改问题。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-067.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/570","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19447","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0674.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0674","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0674.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0674.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-q8cp-g8hf-5jjj/GHSA-q8cp-g8hf-5jjj.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/andreafioraldi/ToolsForCyberChallenge/blob/197d3dfd204cf1b9d1af1451455c8831c3ff9948/generated/files_0.list.dict","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0674.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0216.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0220","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0220.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0676","title":"Sun Solaris 2.6 sdtcm_convert 本地符号链接文件覆盖漏洞","description":"Solaris 2.6 系统中的 sdtcm_convert 工具在处理临时文件时未进行充分的路径安全检查，存在符号链接（symlink）竞争条件漏洞。本地攻击者可通过创建恶意的符号链接，诱使 sdtcm_convert 以特权进程身份覆写任意系统文件，从而导致敏感文件被破坏、权限提升或系统崩溃。该漏洞影响 Solaris 2.6 操作系统，攻击者需拥有本地用户账户权限，攻击复杂度较低，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0676"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:49.510","remediation":"立即安装 Sun Security Bulletin #00151 提供的 Solaris 2.6 官方补丁：SPARC 平台安装 105868-xx 系列补丁（最终版 105868-24），x86 平台安装 105869-xx 系列补丁（最终版 105869-21）。由于 Solaris 2.6 已终止技术支持（EOL），强烈建议升级至受支持的 Oracle Solaris 11.x 或更高版本以获取持续安全更新。如无法立即打补丁或升级，可临时移除 sdtcm_convert 的 setuid 权限（`chmod -s /usr/dt/bin/sdtcm_convert`）并确保 /tmp 等临时目录设置 sticky bit，限制非授权本地用户的 CDE 工具集访问。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/575","http://www.securityfocus.com/templates/archive.pike?list=1&msg=19990809134220.A1191%40hades.chaoz.org","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/77be9686a381151781bc75b69de578b4d9528aae/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0676.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0676","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0676.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0676.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-96rr-v4m6-cxx3/GHSA-96rr-v4m6-cxx3.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/nomi-sec/NVD-Database/blob/23dc120c34402aaa65883c51c1d03b3cb02c20cb/1999/CVE-1999-0676.json","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/oasis-open/cti-stix-common-objects/blob/55ba7598cbd5a52577b6887871505d931d85cb61/objects/vulnerability/vulnerability--5088ae3b-1fe3-4296-b335-fed943d90602.json","https://github.com/VulnerabilityHistoryProject/mega-foss/blob/4829eeb7b0101570abbc87d2a697f2c0c2f4e5c3/src/cve/graphql/trial.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0220.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0233","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0233.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0680","title":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 认证前资源消耗拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Microsoft Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 在处理客户端新建连接请求时，在完成身份认证前会执行额外的资源分配操作，远程攻击者可通过发送大量未认证的连接请求消耗服务器资源，导致终端服务响应缓慢或完全停止响应，造成拒绝服务。该漏洞影响 Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 版本，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0680"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-09T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.027","remediation":"立即安装 Microsoft 安全公告 MS99-028（KB Q238600）提供的补丁。Windows NT 4.0 Terminal Server 已停止技术支持，建议升级至受支持的 Windows Server 版本。临时缓解措施：在防火墙上限制对 TCP 3389 端口的访问，仅允许受信任 IP 连接，并启用终端服务连接认证。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ238600","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-057.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/571","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-028","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/ead50dc12e50bdd7f50b53d9d01c9f9946862c44/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0680.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0680","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/45be3b4afd9c4397ee32a5cbf6819a590220b0c1/content/CVE-1999-0680.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/4ed191c1149de50e461e9a357f4a3a22e603f0d1/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0680.json","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/b7a93df7f7051799495805bc211adea8d202dae7/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-65vm-7q8v-3p23/GHSA-65vm-7q8v-3p23.json","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/intSpLoiT/intframework/blob/eabaa799d0260aa52b735fa9769266d1ce4b64ef/modules/cve_list.txt","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/763b4dfa75aa1890a155aad1b583fdcab8111c49/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0680.json","https://github.com/leego972/titanai/blob/afa5b2310463aae5781d3fd9408071bf38e79806/data/raw/corpus_D_cyber/nvd_cve_000723.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0233.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0218","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0218.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0675","title":"Check Point FireWall-1 VPN-1 UDP 端口 0 拒绝服务漏洞","description":"Check Point FireWall-1 及 VPN-1 产品在处理目标端口号为 0 的 UDP 数据包时存在缺陷，攻击者只需向受保护网络发送特制的 UDP 端口 0 数据包，即可引发防火墙崩溃或拒绝服务，导致合法流量无法被正常过滤与转发。该漏洞利用条件简单，无需身份认证，远程攻击者可通过网络直接触发，对边界防护设备构成严重威胁，影响网络可用性。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0675"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-09","updated":"2026-07-16","remediation":"升级到 Check Point FireWall-1 4.1 Service Pack 2 或更高版本，该版本已修复此 UDP 端口 0 拒绝服务漏洞。若无法立即升级，可在防火墙规则中添加丢弃目标端口为 0 的 UDP 数据包的规则作为临时缓解，并联系 Check Point 获取官方补丁。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/1038","http://www.securityfocus.com/archive/1/23615","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/576","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/main/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0675.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/525.txt"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0218.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0409","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0409.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0722","title":"Cobalt RaQ2 默认配置远程代码执行漏洞","description":"Cobalt RaQ2 服务器默认配置存在安全缺陷，未对远程用户的软件包安装权限进行有效限制。攻击者无需身份认证即可通过默认开放的远程管理接口向服务器安装任意软件包，进而获得服务器的完全控制权。该漏洞严重影响所有采用默认配置的 Cobalt RaQ2 设备，可导致数据泄露、服务中断等严重后果。建议管理员立即修改默认配置并限制远程访问权限。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0722"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-08T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.193","remediation":"立即登录 Cobalt RaQ2 管理控制台，在 \"System Administration > Remote Package Installation\" 中取消勾选 \"Allow remote installation\"，然后应用保存。在防火墙层面，限制对 TCP 81 端口（管理界面）的访问来源仅为受信任的管理 IP 段。由于该产品已停止维护，建议将服务迁移至受支持的 Linux 发行版（如 CentOS/RHEL 替代方案）。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/558"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0409.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0212","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0212.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0673","title":"CREAR ALMail32 POP3 客户端缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"CREAR ALMail32 1.10 POP3 客户端在解析邮件头时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向目标用户发送特制的包含超长 From 或 To 头的电子邮件触发该漏洞，导致拒绝服务或任意代码执行。攻击条件为需要诱使用户使用受影响的客户端接收并查看恶意邮件。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0673"],"sources":["cve","avd"],"published":"1999-08-08","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该漏洞影响 CREAR ALMail32 1.10 及更早版本，厂商已停止维护且无官方补丁。建议立即停用 ALMail32，迁移至现代受支持的 POP3 客户端（如 Mozilla Thunderbird、Claws Mail），并在邮件服务器网关侧配置过滤异常超长 From/To 邮件头字段的规则作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/574","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19450","https://github.com/github/advisory-database/blob/3f4ce19e2c9952be92df5da9390e93383644298b/advisories/unreviewed/2022/04/GHSA-g7pc-52xr-cv98/GHSA-g7pc-52xr-cv98.json"],"poc_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19450"],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19450"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0212.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0239","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0682","title":"Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 SMTP 邮件中继安全绕过漏洞","description":"Microsoft Exchange 5.5 存在电子邮件中继绕过漏洞。远程攻击者可以利用封装的 SMTP 地址格式（如\"<user@domain.com>\"嵌入在邮件地址字段中）发送邮件，即使服务器已启用防中继功能，仍能绕过限制将邮件中继到外部域。该漏洞可被垃圾邮件发送者利用来发送大量垃圾邮件，导致服务器被滥用为开放中继。影响 Microsoft Exchange Server 5.5 版本，攻击无需认证，仅需构造特制邮件地址即可触发。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0682"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:50.280","remediation":"安装 Microsoft Security Bulletin MS99-027 提供的 Exchange Server 5.5 安全更新，该补丁使封装的 SMTP 地址同样受反中继保护。若无法安装补丁，可在 Internet Mail Service 属性中将中继权限限制为仅允许经过身份验证的用户，并禁用不必要的站点到站点 SMTP 中继功能。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://support.microsoft.com/default.aspx?scid=kb%3B%5BLN%5D%3BQ237927","http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-056.shtml","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/567","https://docs.microsoft.com/en-us/security-updates/securitybulletins/1999/ms99-027"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0239.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0322","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0322.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0727","title":"OpenBSD 内核 IPsec 数据加密绕过漏洞","description":"OpenBSD 内核存在信息泄露漏洞，由于内核在处理 IPsec 加密时未正确管理内存或密钥数据，导致部分 IPsec 数据包可能以明文形式发送。远程攻击者可通过网络嗅探方式捕获这些未加密的数据包，获取其中的敏感通信内容，破坏 IPsec 本应提供的机密性保护。该漏洞影响 OpenBSD 操作系统，CVSS 评分 5.0，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0727"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-06T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:55.840","remediation":"立即下载 OpenBSD 官方补丁 009_ipsec_in_use.patch（位于 ftp.openbsd.org/pub/OpenBSD/patches/2.5/common/），执行 cd /usr/src && patch -p0 < 009_ipsec_in_use.patch 后重新编译内核。或直接升级至 OpenBSD 2.6 及以上版本，该版本已合入此修复。如无法立即升级，建议在关键网关上禁用 IPsec 隧道或限制对 IPsec SA 管理接口的访问作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.osvdb.org/6127"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0322.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0319","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0319.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0719","title":"GNOME Gnumeric Guile 插件代码执行漏洞","description":"Gnumeric 电子表格软件中的 Guile 插件存在代码执行漏洞。攻击者可通过构造恶意的电子表格文件，诱使用户在受影响版本中打开该文件，从而触发该漏洞并执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Gnumeric 的受影响版本，攻击复杂度较高，需要用户交互配合，CVSS 评分 4.6，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":4.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0719"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-05T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:54.830","remediation":"升级至 Gnumeric 0.50 及以上版本，该版本已移除存在安全风险的 Guile 插件扩展支持。对于无法升级的系统，直接删除或禁用 Guile 插件文件（如 gnumeric-guile.so），并移除 gnumeric 对 libguile 的依赖调用，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/563"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0319.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-1300","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-1300.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0913","title":"Network Security Wizards Dragon-Fire IDS 远程命令执行漏洞","description":"Dragon-Fire IDS 1.0 的 dfire.cgi 脚本存在命令注入漏洞，远程攻击者可通过在 HTTP 请求参数中插入 shell 元字符（如分号、管道符等）来执行任意系统命令。该漏洞影响 Network Security Wizards 公司出品的 Dragon-Fire IDS 1.0 版本，无需认证即可远程触发，CVSS 评分 10.0，危害等级严重。","severity":"CRITICAL","score":10.0,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0913"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-05","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"该产品已停止维护，建议禁用 dfire.cgi 脚本或限制其访问来源。如无法禁用，在 Web 服务器层面对所有用户输入过滤 shell 元字符（;|&`$），并配置防火墙仅允许可信 IP 访问 Dragon-Fire IDS 管理界面。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://marc.info/?l=bugtraq&m=93383593909438&w=2","http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/564","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19444"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":["https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19444"],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-1300.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0204","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0671","title":"ToxSoft NextFTP 远程缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"ToxSoft NextFTP 1.82 客户端存在缓冲区溢出漏洞，远程攻击者可通过向 FTP 服务器发送特制的 CWD（Change Working Directory）命令触发该漏洞，导致目标系统上的 NextFTP 客户端程序崩溃或执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 NextFTP 1.82 版本，攻击者需诱骗用户连接至恶意 FTP 服务器，利用难度中等。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0671"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.857","remediation":"ToxSoft 已停止运营，官方未发布补丁。建议立即停止使用 NextFTP 1.82，迁移至仍受维护的 FTP 客户端（如 FileZilla、WinSCP）。如暂时无法替换，可通过网络防火墙或 IPS 规则拦截包含超长 CWD 命令的 FTP 请求，作为临时缓解措施。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/572","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19448","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0671.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0671","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0671.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/f6ced4f7862026f4207c9708deb4edf129c83fc5/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0671.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/308.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0671.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.224","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0204.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0285","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0285.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0703","title":"OpenBSD/BSDI Unix chflags/fchflags 特殊设备文件权限管理漏洞","description":"OpenBSD、BSDI 及其他类 Unix 操作系统中，普通用户可对字符设备和块设备文件调用 chflags 及 fchflags 系统调用来修改文件标志位。该漏洞允许非特权本地用户更改设备文件的不可变标志（如 schg、uappend 等），可能导致设备文件属性被非授权篡改，进而绕过系统安全策略。攻击者需拥有本地 shell 访问权限才能利用此漏洞，无法远程触发。","severity":"LOW","score":3.6,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0703"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-03T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:52.917","remediation":"建议安装 OpenBSD 2.5/2.6 及 BSDI 相应版本的安全补丁，限制普通用户对字符设备和块设备执行 chflags/fchflags 操作。如无法升级，可通过内核参数或 LKM 禁用非特权用户的 chflags 系统调用，或在系统关键设备节点上移除用户写权限作为临时缓解。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-13T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.ciac.org/ciac/bulletins/j-066.shtml"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0285.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0224","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0224.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0677","title":"Ramp Networks WebRamp Web 管理默认口令漏洞","description":"WebRamp 200i 与 M3 网络设备的 Web 管理界面存在默认口令漏洞，设备出厂时预置了未强制修改的管理员默认密码。远程攻击者只需通过网络访问管理端口，使用默认凭据即可登录并获得设备完全管理权限，进而可修改网络配置、窃取通信数据或发起中间人攻击。该漏洞风险等级高，影响范围广泛，且利用难度极低。","severity":"HIGH","score":7.5,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0677"],"sources":["cve"],"published":"1999-08-03","updated":"2026-06-16","remediation":"Ramp Networks WebRamp 200i/M3 路由器出厂预置默认管理员密码且未强制用户修改，攻击者可直接通过 Web 管理界面登录获取完全控制权。由于该产品已停止维护多年无安全更新，建议立即登录管理界面修改默认密码，在防火墙限制仅白名单 IP 可访问 Web 管理端口（80/443）；若设备仍在生产环境使用，应尽快替换为仍在安全支持周期内的替代产品。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-16T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/577","https://nvd.nist.gov/vuln/detail/CVE-1999-0677"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0224.toml"},{"ave_id":"AVE-1999-0211","file_name":"1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml","cve_id":"CVE-1999-0672","title":"Fujitsu Chocoa IRC 客户端 Topic 缓冲区溢出漏洞","description":"Fujitsu Chocoa IRC 客户端在处理 IRC 频道主题（Topic）时存在缓冲区溢出漏洞。远程攻击者可通过向运行该客户端的用户发送特制的畸形频道主题数据，触发缓冲区溢出，导致客户端崩溃或可能执行任意代码。该漏洞影响 Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R 版本，CVSS 评分 5.1，危害等级中危。","severity":"MEDIUM","score":5.1,"aliases":["CVE-1999-0672"],"sources":["avd"],"published":"1999-08-01T04:00:00.000","updated":"2026-06-16T21:48:48.990","remediation":"Fujitsu Chocoa 1.0 beta7R 已停止维护，官方未发布修复版本。建议立即停止使用该客户端，迁移至仍在维护的 IRC 客户端（如 mIRC、HexChat、Irssi）。作为临时缓解措施，可在 IRC 服务器端或客户端配置中过滤/禁用自动解析频道主题，避免触发缓冲区溢出。","status":"completed","collected_at":"2026-07-14T00:00:00Z","references":["http://www.securityfocus.com/bid/573","https://www.exploit-db.com/exploits/19449","https://github.com/CVEProject/cvelistV5/blob/b8581edcbd9fb1606112c43470d0a7cb92a751f8/cves/1999/0xxx/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/LiuCan01/cve-list-pro/blob/78b55511cee3604c22d518e32822f0435d0cacc0/cve-list/CVE-1999/CVE-1999-0672","https://github.com/yarencheng/cve-devops-playground/blob/9074597bd191efd66c2a6bf1f5d8e60bc4801a90/content/CVE-1999-0672.md","https://github.com/Patrowl/PatrowlHearsData/blob/0fec8c5c64ee33c93da01ddd0b28bf8f9f743a61/CVE/data/1999/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/eldondev/Snort/blob/34bdcf6a7a638b55c7c04f77ef1efa526ad08e33/doc/signatures/307.txt","https://github.com/rhuitl/uClinux/blob/0486e80a025dccbe4a2213715a2ab8a5063ea86b/user/snort/drop-rules/exploit.rules","https://github.com/feng-li/tools-for-data-science-course/blob/8e62d47ee8ffbebe9a0e50aee193617f83883118/2019spring/2017312271/result.txt","https://github.com/olbat/nvdcve/blob/d21eb36f6164170df89822577def7df5351966d2/nvdcve/CVE-1999-0672.json","https://github.com/slacker247/GPDA/blob/fa9006d0877a691f1ddffe88799c844a3e8a669a/Sodi/Run/IDSrules/rule.223","https://github.com/KTZgraph/sarenka/blob/f1fb931ab722d6c096d581ed6e3c5966d799fbaa/sarenka/feeds/cve_details/cve_all_details_153500_153600.json"],"poc_urls":[],"exp_urls":[],"repo_poc_urls":[],"repo_exp_urls":[],"has_poc":false,"has_exp":false,"raw_url":"https://github.com/adysec/AVE/blob/main/vulns/1999/AVE-1999-0211.toml"}]